Enum AccessFlag

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AccessFlag>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<AccessFlag>
    public enum AccessFlag
extends Enum<AccessFlag>
    Access flags are mask of flags used to denote access permissions to and properties of this class file.
    Author:
    Amos Shi 
     java:S2386 - Mutable fields should not be "public static" --- We keep the simplied public variable
